Lord Jamar sat down for another session with DJ Vlad to give his hot takes on current events happening in the media. He discussed Tyrese's behavior on social media, Amber Rose & Blac Chyna dating younger men, how the judicial system has failed Meek Mill and hoards of others like him, and why he believes Royce da 5'9" is a better rapper than Eminem. 

Watch the full interview above.
